[
    {
        "content": "<p>Currently trying to on a DMI abstraction (have quite a lot working). Main problem right now is how can I initialize the bitfield in <code>dmi_strmatch</code> in a const context (need const for the alias kernel exports). The functions bindgen generates are all not const, and otherwise I can construct the bitfield from hand, but according to what I find the bitfield order is implementation definde, so that it might be wrong if I just do manual bitshifts</p>",
        "id": 488604186,
        "sender_full_name": "Fiona Behrens",
        "timestamp": 1734000833
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Do you have a concrete example so that we discuss it here? Could <code>bindgen</code> potentially generate them (or something else) already <code>const</code>?</p>",
        "id": 488605887,
        "sender_full_name": "Miguel Ojeda",
        "timestamp": 1734001332
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Concret example would be <code>slot</code> in the C struct <code>dmi_strmatch</code>. Right now bindgens implementation of those bitfield things uses <code>as_ref</code> and <code>as_mut</code> (and also other mutable references) so I think bindgen would have to change the internal implementations to fix this. all I really would need is that the <code>new_bitfield_1</code>  function on the bindgen dmi_strmatch is const and that bindgen would change how that function works internally for that.</p>",
        "id": 488606736,
        "sender_full_name": "Fiona Behrens",
        "timestamp": 1734001615
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>right now doing this in my wrapper newtype (tuple struct), but think this is not endinaness safe (also include copying the name here but that is a different topic)</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">const</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">new_with_exact</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">slot</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Field</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">substr</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"kt\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">bool</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Self</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">bitfield</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">else</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">})</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;&lt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">7</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">slot</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">as</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">u8</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">this</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">bindings</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">dmi_strmatch</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">_bitfield_1</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">bindings</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">__BindgenBitfieldUnit</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">new</span><span class=\"p\">([</span><span class=\"n\">bitfield</span><span class=\"p\">]),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ZERO</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">});</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">input</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">substr</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">as_bytes</span><span class=\"p\">();</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">input</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">len</span><span class=\"p\">();</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"k\">loop</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">this</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"mf\">0.</span><span class=\"n\">substr</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">index</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">input</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">index</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">as</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">i8</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">==</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"k\">break</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">this</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 488606897,
        "sender_full_name": "Fiona Behrens",
        "timestamp": 1734001674
    },
    {
        "content": "<blockquote>\n<p>all I really would need is that the <code>new_bitfield_1</code> function on the bindgen dmi_strmatch is const and that bindgen would change how that function works internally for that.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Could you please paste that part of the <code>bindgen</code>-generated code and the C definition? i.e. to see if <code>bindgen</code> could generate what you need (since that it is usually ideal, eventually).</p>\n<p>Cc <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"750526\">@Christian Poveda</span> <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"447074\">@John Baublitz</span> in case they are interested</p>",
        "id": 488608983,
        "sender_full_name": "Miguel Ojeda",
        "timestamp": 1734002368
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It's over many different places, but sure:<br>\nC:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"C\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">dmi_strmatch</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"kt\">unsigned</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">char</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">slot</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">7</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"kt\">unsigned</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">char</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">exact_match</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"kt\">char</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">substr</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">79</span><span class=\"p\">];</span>\n<span class=\"p\">};</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Bindgen bitfield type</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"cp\">#[repr(C)]</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#[derive(Copy, Clone, Debug, Default, Eq, Hash, Ord, PartialEq, PartialOrd)]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">__BindgenBitfieldUnit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Storage</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">storage</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Storage</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Storage</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">__BindgenBitfieldUnit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Storage</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"cp\">#[inline]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">const</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">new</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">storage</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Storage</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Self</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">storage</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Storage</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">__BindgenBitfieldUnit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Storage</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"k\">where</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">Storage</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">AsRef</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">u8</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">AsMut</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">u8</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"cp\">#[inline]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">get_bit</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">index</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">usize</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">bool</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"fm\">debug_assert!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">8</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">storage</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">as_ref</span><span class=\"p\">().</span><span class=\"n\">len</span><span class=\"p\">());</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">byte_index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">8</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">byte</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">storage</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">as_ref</span><span class=\"p\">()[</span><span class=\"n\">byte_index</span><span class=\"p\">];</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">bit_index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"fm\">cfg!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">target_endian</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"big\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"mi\">7</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">%</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">8</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">else</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">%</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">8</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">};</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mask</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;&lt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">bit_index</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">byte</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mask</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">==</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mask</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"cp\">#[inline]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">set_bit</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">index</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">usize</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">bool</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"fm\">debug_assert!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">8</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">storage</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">as_ref</span><span class=\"p\">().</span><span class=\"n\">len</span><span class=\"p\">());</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">byte_index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">8</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">byte</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span 